<section xmlns:codified="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codified" xmlns:codify="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codify" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" containing-doc="D.C. Code">
  <num>32-708</num>
  <heading>Recordkeeping requirements.</heading>
  <para>
    <num>(a)</num>
    <text>The Mayor shall maintain adequate records of declarations of domestic partnership, termination statements, and amendments to declarations of domestic partnership and termination statements.</text>
  </para>
  <para>
    <num>(b)</num>
    <text>The Mayor shall report annually to the Council on the number of domestic partnerships declared and terminated, including those terminated under § <cite path="§32-702">32-702</cite> (d)(5).</text>
  </para>
